<div id="c6">
<p>Its slightly misleading to state that the world discovered that missile defense wouldn&#8217;t work until Sakharov started talking about it. Groups such as the American Physical Society published a number large of reports on the feasibility of star wars that were politically quite influential. The APS reports stated that star wars were unlikely to work.</p>

<p>You can read a bit about the report at</p>

<p>http://sciencereview.berkeley.edu/articles.php?issue=9&amp;article=missile-defense</p>

